                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6741" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1055</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9065 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">疯狂扩张，满“债”而归——华夏幸福债务违约及自救之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Crazy expansion, full of &quot;debt&quot;——The Debt Default and Self-Saving Road of CFLD</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒲丹琳，郭桂芳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华夏幸福基业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华夏幸福；债务危机；财务风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> CFLD; Debt crisis; Financial risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为产业新城业务模式重要的开创者，华夏幸福曾经风光无限。从2002年第一项产业新城PPP项目落地，便开启了产业新城异地快速复制模式，可观的收益使其扩张进程愈演愈烈，然而，2017年起，接连受到房地产政策调控以及疫情冲击，终于在2021年全面爆发债务危机。本案例详细描述华夏幸福进行高速扩张，随之在宏观环境不利的形势下最终陷入债务危机的过程，并阐述华夏幸福陷入债务危机的种种迹象以及其应对债务危机采取的自救措施，使学员了解如何识别企业的债务危机，并学会分析其产生原因，引导学生思考化解债务危机的办法，思考在“三道红线”限制下房地产企业应如何避免和防范债务危机。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the most important pioneer of the business model of industrial new town, CFLD once enjoyed unlimited success. Since 2002, when the first PPP project of the new industrial city was implemented, the rapid replication mode of the new industrial city was started. The considerable income made its expansion process intensified. However, since 2017, it has been affected by the real estate policy regulation and epidemic, and finally broke out in 2021. Detailed description high-speed expansion of CFLD in this case, then at the macro environment unfavorable situation, the process of falling into debt crisis, and the indications of a debt crisis and its self rescue measures, make the students know how to identify the enterprise&#39;s debt crisis and to analyze its causes,and guide students to think about the solution to the debt crisis, consider how to avoid and prevent the debt crisis in the real estate enterprises under the restriction of &quot;three red lines&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理学》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开发性PPP模式的涵义；产业新城的运营模式；过度扩张的概念；过度扩张带来的财务后果；债务危机的涵义；企业债务危机的成因；债务危机的化解措施；房地产行业经营特点与财务特点</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
